{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CBCentralManager"},{"type":"text","text":" handles accessing Bluetooth, discovering devices, and managing connections."}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SitePoint devices are Bluetooth peripherals. In Bluetooth terms, this means they are connected from a Bluetooth central device — a mobile device running an app, in this case."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once a SitePoint is connected, "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B4_CBPeripheral"},{"type":"text","text":" accesses its SignalQuest services."}]},{"anchor":"Reference-the-example-app","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Reference the example app"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the SitePoint iOS Example App, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CBCentralManager"},{"type":"text","text":" code is in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Bluetooth.swift"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file also creates a delegate extension that conforms to  "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CBCentralManagerDelegate"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"style":"tip","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This file contains some helper functions which aren’t mentioned below or required, such as a timer that handles removing stale devices from the list of previously found devices."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Tip"},{"anchor":"Scanning-for-SitePoint-peripherals","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Scanning for SitePoint peripherals"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In the example app, the scanning starts as soon as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centralManager"},{"type":"text","text":" is available. The scan is initiated within the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centralManagerDidUpdateState"},{"type":"text","text":" callback."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The scan specifies a filter on service UUID using "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"withServices:"},{"type":"text","text":" to only return devices with the SitePoint service UUID of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"00000100-34ed-12ef-63f4-317792041d17"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func centralManagerDidUpdateState(_ central: CBCentralManager) {","    if central.state != .poweredOn {","        displayError(\"CBCentralManager is not powered on\")","    } else {","        centralManager?.scanForPeripherals(withServices: [SitePointPeripheral.sitePointServiceUuid], options: [CBCentralManagerScanOptionAllowDuplicatesKey : true])","        BluetoothManager.logger.info(\"Started scanning\")","    }","}"]},{"anchor":"Handling-discovered-SitePoint-peripherals","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Handling discovered SitePoint peripherals"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When a scan finds a peripheral with the SitePoint Service UUID, it returns the peripheral using the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centralManager.didDiscover"},{"type":"text","text":" callback."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example app uses this callback to build a list of found SitePoint peripherals along with some manufacturer data, from the related scan response."}]},{"style":"note","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The example app also keeps a list of timestamps for each found peripheral. This is not required, but may be helpful to avoid stale devices remaining in the list. This is paired with a timer to do a stale device check and cleanup."}]}],"type":"aside","name":"Note"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func centralManager(_ central: CBCentralManager, didDiscover peripheral: CBPeripheral, advertisementData: [String: Any], rssi RSSI: NSNumber) {","    devicesToWhenFound[peripheral] = Date()","    devicesToScanStatus[peripheral] = getScanStatus(advertisementData)","}"]},{"anchor":"Connecting-to-a-SitePoint-peripheral","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Connecting to a SitePoint peripheral"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Connect to a SitePoint by calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centralManager.connect"},{"type":"text","text":" and passing in the peripheral to connect."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Once connected, the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centralManager.didConnect"},{"type":"text","text":" callback will be called."}]},{"anchor":"Initiate-service-discovery","level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Initiate service discovery"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"From the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"centralManager.didConnect"},{"type":"text","text":" callback, call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"discoverServices"},{"type":"text","text":" on the peripheral to initiate the querying of services and their characteristics."}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func centralManager(_ central: CBCentralManager, didConnect peripheral: CBPeripheral) {","    AppDelegate.instance.sitePoint.didConnect(peripheral)","    peripheral.discoverServices(nil)","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"These queries, along with additional handling for reading and writing data, are handled by "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CBPeripheral"},{"type":"text","text":" which is covered in the next section."}]},{"anchor":"Read-Next","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Read Next"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B4_CBPeripheral"}]}]}]}]}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"sections":[],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/sitepointsdk\/b3_cbcentralmanager"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B3_CBCentralManager","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set up "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CBCentralManager"},{"type":"text","text":" to scan for and connect to SitePoint Bluetooth devices."}],"kind":"article","metadata":{"roleHeading":"Article","title":"CBCentralManager","role":"article","modules":[{"name":"SitePointSdk"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk"]]},"seeAlsoSections":[{"title":"Implementation","identifiers":["doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B1_Implementation-Guide","doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B2_Permissions","doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B4_CBPeripheral","doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B5_NTRIP"],"generated":true}],"references":{"doc://SitePointSdk/documentation/SitePointSdk":{"role":"collection","title":"SitePointSdk","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Provides an API and utilities for interfacing with SignalQuest’s SitePoint GNSS devices."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/sitepointsdk"},"doc://SitePointSdk/documentation/SitePointSdk/B2_Permissions":{"role":"article","title":"Permissions","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add permissions for Bluetooth and Location services."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B2_Permissions","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/sitepointsdk\/b2_permissions"},"doc://SitePointSdk/documentation/SitePointSdk/B4_CBPeripheral":{"role":"article","title":"CBPeripheral","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set up CBPeripheral to interface with a connected SitePoint Bluetooth device."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B4_CBPeripheral","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/sitepointsdk\/b4_cbperipheral"},"doc://SitePointSdk/documentation/SitePointSdk/B5_NTRIP":{"role":"article","title":"NTRIP","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Set up NTRIP connection handling and RTCM parsing for aiding the SitePoint."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B5_NTRIP","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/sitepointsdk\/b5_ntrip"},"doc://SitePointSdk/documentation/SitePointSdk/B1_Implementation-Guide":{"role":"article","title":"Implementation Guide","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Review example app code to use the SitePoint SDK with Bluetooth and NTRIP."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/SitePointSdk\/documentation\/SitePointSdk\/B1_Implementation-Guide","kind":"article","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/sitepointsdk\/b1_implementation-guide"}}}